    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The world is falling apart. Monsters that were once people stalk the streets. Food is running out, people are dying. Hope is lost.<br><br>You alone carry the spark that can bring light to peoples hearts once again, and burn away monstrosities.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Beware, you're being hunted. Strange and deadly horrors hide behind every corner. Armed with only an axe and your wits, face the horrors and find the answers you seek.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/8b37dbf365c8134c9917fb7e885fb698.poster.avif?t=1767536231\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/8b37dbf365c8134c9917fb7e885fb698.webm?t=1767536231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/8b37dbf365c8134c9917fb7e885fb698.mp4?t=1767536231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES </h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Directional, Grid-Based Combat -</strong> Brutal grid-based combat with directional attacking and blocking that requires both quick reflexes and strategic thinking. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Choices Matter - </strong>Be careful on you route through  Frozen Pines, your actions will affect will affect whether characters live or die.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A Love Letter to PS2 Horror</strong> - Inspired by the likes of Killer7, King's Field 4, and the Silent Hill series, with a unique retro horror aesthetic. </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Chilling Monster Encounters - </strong>Explore a variety of eerie locations and eldritch beasts as you search for survivors, uncovering the source of the calamity.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/2e95b032a4e3a882b726853bd8de6a48.poster.avif?t=1767536231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/2e95b032a4e3a882b726853bd8de6a48.webm?t=1767536231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/2e95b032a4e3a882b726853bd8de6a48.mp4?t=1767536231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >_____________________________________________________________________</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/bc0c09d00e9cbe47f278c28d127b526e.poster.avif?t=1767536231\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/bc0c09d00e9cbe47f278c28d127b526e.webm?t=1767536231\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3122000/extras/bc0c09d00e9cbe47f278c28d127b526e.mp4?t=1767536231\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
